M.A.C Cosmetics's John Demsey and His Busy Social Life
Keeping up the cool quotient by keeping a packed calendar

 






By

Ray A. Smith


Ray A. Smith
The Wall Street Journal
BiographyRay A. Smith
@rayalexsmith
Ray.Smith@wsj.com




  Feb. 12, 2014 7:01 p.m. ET





 John Demsey's social calendar is so complicated that an assistant's sole responsibility is managing it. Mr. Demsey, who oversees M.A.C Cosmetics, receives six to seven social invitations a day. He goes out four nights a week, often to several events a night. It is all in the service of keeping M.A.C cool and current, and at Mr. Demsey's age (56) and M.A.C's age (30), that's a lot of work. The bold cosmetics brand, part of Est√©e...
  


