‚ÄúI see things on the hanger and I‚Äôm, like, ‚ÄòI never knew that color worked on me.‚Äô It‚Äôs things you necessarily wouldn‚Äôt choose to wear, but once you put them on, you see why Janie is who Janie is." ‚Äî Lily Collins on working with former "Mad Men" costume designer, Janie Bryant on creating looks for her role as Celia Brady's in Amazon series, "The Last Tycoon." üì∏@jilliansollazzo  #wwdeye





